{"tid":1040140,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"范國威聽預算案開電腦搵相　點解會係張栢芝？","createTime":"2019-02-28T01:10:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-28T01:24:02.000Z","uid":13468,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d601653c79fe59f0cb6441bbd0a8545c4f945885","tid":1040140,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T01:10:15.000Z","msg":"范國威聽預算案開電腦搵相 點解會係張栢芝？<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190227/s00001/1551265262194/%E3%80%90emily-online%E3%80%91%E8%8C%83%E5%9C%8B%E5%A8%81%E8%81%BD%E9%A0%90%E7%AE%97%E6%A1%88%E9%96%8B%E9%9B%BB%E8%85%A6%E6%90%B5%E7%9B%B8-%E9%BB%9E%E8%A7%A3%E6%9C%83%E4%BF%82%E5%BC%B5%E6%A0%A2%E8%8A%9D\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190227%2Fs00001%2F1551265262194%2F%25E3%2580%2590emily-online%25E3%2580%2591%25E8%258C%2583%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2581%25BD%25E9%25A0%2590%25E7%25AE%2597%25E6%25A1%2588%25E9%2596%258B%25E9%259B%25BB%25E8%2585%25A6%25E6%2590%25B5%25E7%259B%25B8-%25E9%25BB%259E%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E6%259C%2583%25E4%25BF%2582%25E5%25BC%25B5%25E6%25A0%25A2%25E8%258A%259D&d=HVFDXqn9keSrFxh6Mt7TdzyMEfxyOVmMxalVp7jK43I%3D&h=72619fcf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190227%2Fs00001%2F1551265262194%2F%25E3%2580%2590emily-online%25E3%2580%2591%25E8%258C%2583%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2581%25BD%25E9%25A0%2590%25E7%25AE%2597%25E6%25A1%2588%25E9%2596%258B%25E9%259B%25BB%25E8%2585%25A6%25E6%2590%25B5%25E7%259B%25B8-%25E9%25BB%259E%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E6%259C%2583%25E4%25BF%2582%25E5%25BC%25B5%25E6%25A0%25A2%25E8%258A%259D&h=9cdfbaf1\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190227/s00001/1551265262194/%E3%80%90emily-online%E3%80%91%E8%8C%83%E5%9C%8B%E5%A8%81%E8%81%BD%E9%A0%90%E7%AE%97%E6%A1%88%E9%96%8B%E9%9B%BB%E8%85%A6%E6%90%B5%E7%9B%B8-%E9%BB%9E%E8%A7%A3%E6%9C%83%E4%BF%82%E5%BC%B5%E6%A0%A2%E8%8A%9D</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190227/s00001/d20d72f5e7d30774f00083db4f04c789.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190227%2Fs00001%2Fd20d72f5e7d30774f00083db4f04c789.jpg&h=94a559fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n財政司長陳茂波今朝喺立法會宣讀《財政預算案》歷時接近兩個鐘，議員聽嗰陣未必完全專心，有議員疑似恰眼瞓，亦有人撳電話，其間新民主同盟范國威（Gary）嘅電腦熒幕搜尋頁面，出現多張藝人張栢芝嘅照片，部分較為性感，呢一幕就被Emily嘅攝影同事影到，同時亦見到佢搵財爺照片、牛隻照片，種類相當多元化，但Gary都冇撳入去睇啲相。<br />\n<br />\n到底Gary搵緊啲咩會出現呢啲照片？Gary就解釋，新民主同盟嘅道具都係由佢製作，當時佢諗緊回應《財政預算案》嘅主題，所以喺Google搜尋咗「貓哭老鼠假慈悲」、「九牛一毛」等關鍵字，希望搵吓圖片製作道具，所以只係做緊公務。及後Gary喺記者會上回應預算案時，就以「基建揮金如土，民生九牛一毛」去做主題，但圖片就只有棒型圖，未見採用佢喺會議廳內搜尋嘅牛等。<br />\n<br />\nGary為表清白，更立即畀Emily睇，當時佢輸入「貓哭老鼠假慈悲」搜尋圖片時，喺較後頁數就出現咗張栢芝嘅性感照片，佢亦強調一出現唔關事嘅照片，已經立即碌走咗。<br />\n<br />\nEmily其後都試過喺Google搜尋「貓哭老鼠假慈悲」，喺較後嘅相片的確出現唔少張栢芝嘅圖片。翻查報道，張栢芝幾年前曾經受訪，曾以「貓哭老鼠假慈悲」批評藝人陳冠希嘅言論。"},{"pid":"3ed47f18bab4c82a6f6118555fe7d928c53a698b","tid":1040140,"uid":56698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T01:13:18.000Z","msg":"做緊勞作交功課啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c6d9a63cd4dfade8df90a102c38030da5d1a8e5","tid":1040140,"uid":47674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T01:22:03.000Z","msg":"左上嗰張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"966b5c402e9f6f3065e2ae1c53042a8aaed3e4f1","tid":1040140,"uid":4739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c6d9a63cd4dfade8df90a102c38030da5d1a8e5","tid":1040140,"uid":47674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T01:22:03.000Z","msg":"左上嗰張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T01:24:02.000Z","msg":"經典，過年先重溫完"}]}